### Affected Package
The issue is caused by package @angular/forms

### Is this a regression?
Couldn't check.

### Description
Adding only disabled AbstractControl to a FormGroup or a FormArray disables their parent.
Moreover, the "value" field changes its behaviour when all the controls are disabled (showing all of them instead of only the enabled ones)

